---
title: Sweet-Soy Chicken & Garlic Rice with Bacon-Ginger Veggies & Crispy Shallots
description: This fragrant meal packs flavour in every bite. From the garlic rice to the spiced chicken brimming with sweet and savoury notes and the colourful veggies, this is so much better than takeaway!

